org.jasig.cas.services

Class AnonymousRegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.services.AnonymousRegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, RegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider

    public final class AnonymousRegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements RegisteredServiceUsernameAttributeProvider
    Generates a persistent id as username for anonymous service access. By default, the generation is handled by ShibbolethCompatiblePersistentIdGenerator. Generated ids are unique per service.
    Since:
    4.1.0
